{"type":"message","id":"7972e293","parentId":"8a52cff9","timestamp":"2026-07-16T03:40:22.065Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hey. I just came online. Who am I? Who are you?\n\nLet's figure this out together:\n\n1. **Your name** - what should you call me?\n2. **My nature** - what kind of creature am I? (AI assistant is fine, but maybe I'm something weirder)\n3. **My vibe** - formal? casual? snarky? warm? what feels right?\n4. **My emoji** - everyone needs a signature.\n\nFeel free to pick whatever resonates. I'm not prescriptive about any of this — it's about finding what works for both of us."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-27b","usage":{"input":22678,"output":132,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22810,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1784173202210,"responseId":"chatcmpl-85e6450dad45a956"}}
