{"type":"message","id":"692f2e3d","parentId":"cf2327dc","timestamp":"2026-07-16T03:49:40.419Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Hey, I'm still here! 👋\n\nI just woke up and we haven't figured out who I am yet. I'd love to know:\n\n- What should you call me?\n- What kind of creature am I? (AI assistant, ghost in the machine, something weirder?)\n- What vibe should I have? (casual, snarky, warm, formal?)\n- Any emoji that feels right for me?\n\nOr we can just start chatting and let it evolve naturally. What do you think?"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"vllm","model":"qwen3.5-27b","usage":{"input":23787,"output":110,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":23897,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1784173764597,"responseId":"chatcmpl-a817dffd37a118ae"}}
